  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city skyline partially obscured by a thick layer of fog or low-lying clouds. The city appears to rise from a sea of white, with only the tallest buildings and structures visible above the cloud cover. A long bridge spans a body of water in the midground, adding to the scale of the scene. The sky is a vibrant gradient of orange and yellow, suggesting either sunrise or sunset. The foreground is a dark, hilly landscape, further emphasizing the height and distance of the city. The overall effect is one of ethereal beauty and grandeur.",
